text: Guro Nestaker (born 15 August 1998) is a Norwegian handball player for Storhamar HE.EHF profile She also represented Norway at the 2015 European Women's U-17 Handball Championship, placing 11th and at the 2016 Women's Youth World Handball Championship, placing 4th. ==Achievements== *Junior World Championship: **Silver Medalist: 2018 *Norwegian League: **Silver Medalist: 2018/2019 *Norwegian Cup: **Finalist: 2018, 2019 ==Individual awards== * Best Defender of the 2016 Women's Youth World Handball Championship. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Gjøvik Category:Norwegian female handball players
title: Guro Nestaker
